                <ul>
                    <li>This system is suited for intermediate to advanced traders due to its complexity.</li>
                    <li>It involves trailing stops and dynamic take profit levels.</li>
                    <li>Suitable for trading reversals, regular and hidden divergence, and scalping.</li>
                </ul>

